{"tid":866364,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人戴con後睇野對唔到蕉咁？","createTime":"2018-10-17T20:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T10:14:14.000Z","uid":182113,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4c970cb974110212a9c902aea8decc6818bc9fb5","tid":866364,"uid":182113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T20:43:45.000Z","msg":"本身有戴眼鏡，副con照眼鏡近視同散光-20，所以實唔關度數事<br />\n戴左con上眼之後，試左幾日，間中睇野會好清仲爽過戴眼鏡，但好多時間都係好似相機對唔到蕉咁既情況矇查查<br />\n<br />\n我係大鋪配的，D店員都話唔知點解，已經試左三副都係咁，直頭叫我退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會係我對眼有咩問題"},{"pid":"85e1f4a7f8a5ef92468ccd2cd2ff08f0b3190af9","tid":866364,"uid":77314,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T20:49:01.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n用完記住唔好dump馬桶<br />\n利申：保護海龜協會會員"},{"pid":"52d18d10b434603866b4d159330a7e11c36a9c71","tid":866364,"uid":80982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:04:33.000Z","msg":"Con移位好似係 不過大部分時間都唔會 試下碌下個眼珠tune下"},{"pid":"77c83f2241133ae9fe7d162d311433700f9c72fe","tid":866364,"uid":155256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:44:56.000Z","msg":"係咪孤度唔岩呀，好似有啲分8.5、9.0之類，問下個視光師"},{"pid":"9703a086835bb71a722a4d6c23d223df02114e77","tid":866364,"uid":155256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77c83f2241133ae9fe7d162d311433700f9c72fe","tid":866364,"uid":155256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:44:56.000Z","msg":"係咪孤度唔岩呀，好似有啲分8.5、9.0之類，問下個視光師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:45:58.000Z","msg":"弧度 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b9cf3e1175327419e2fa074bcfb9c93e2b479d","tid":866364,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:49:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f32062f1b4e9a340051f4859ffb4f29e397ba241","tid":866364,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T22:40:44.000Z","msg":"me too"},{"pid":"62b1e70cdb5039b04d2ce5ed6503b28022d131ea","tid":866364,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T22:52:30.000Z","msg":"上下帶錯?<br />\n凸出小小果面係上下wo"},{"pid":"f057dcfdeb50662efdf2463e2578e68d5d8270d0","tid":866364,"uid":205539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪眼乾，戴得耐一滴眼藥水就睇唔清"},{"pid":"ac4888a8f9250d3de5afae11aea1a0b8f1c1b7fd","tid":866364,"uid":186765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:04:41.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<br />\n個時眼鏡88條友話散光con 係咁<br />\n我都唔知真唔真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294726c81f47f32bbbfa2e9e0b1cfe5dee2922a4","tid":866364,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"散光con就算帶錯應該碌一碌隻眼會慢慢調翻啱個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪你一開始就戴好耐?<br />\n我去啲小店配佢地叫我戴嘅時間慢慢加上去<br />\n二四六咁加上去 等隻眼習慣啲<br />\n我一開始戴都係有啲濛有啲飄咁<br />\n慢慢增加時數戴 戴多幾次就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}